productTiles.title: Herbed Turkey Breast
productTiles.description:
Schneiders® Herbed Turkey Breast is a favourite for good reason. It all starts with premium turkey breast, coated with oregano, garlic and rosemary and then slowly oven-roasted to bring out the classic turkey flavour you know and love. Now made with 25% less sodium than regular turkey, it delivers absolutely zero compromise on taste. Schneiders® brand has been committed to providing Canadian families with the highest quality of craftsmanship since 1890. Carefully staying true to J.M. Schneider’s original recipes, they use only premium cuts of turkey for a traditional taste you can be proud to share with family and friends. An excellent source of protein, Schneiders® Herbed Turkey breast is a satisfying addition to sandwiches, appetizers and charcuterie boards and comes conveniently sliced in a resealable package for easy serving.

  • Authentic Turkey Taste: Slow oven roasted and perfectly seasoned with oregano, garlic and rosemary.
  • Excellent Source of Protein: Reduced-sodium turkey satisfies with 12g of protein per serving.
  • Share the Love: Schneiders® turkey is a crowd-pleaser on charcuterie boards or sandwich platters.
  • Ready to Eat: Oven-roasted turkey slices come ready to enjoy in a resealable package for easy serving.
  • Crafted without Compromise: Schneiders® deli meats deliver authentic flavour and premium quality.
